WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.625 --> 00:00:09.250
[rain pouring]

2
00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:11.916
[tense music playing]

3
00:00:12.750 --> 00:00:14.875
[Shimura] Goodbye. Asamiya.

4
00:00:17.166 --> 00:00:19.250
Hey! Stop!

5
00:00:29.708 --> 00:00:30.833
Tatsuya!

6
00:00:30.916 --> 00:00:34.250
-[thunder crashing]
-[Shimura splashes]

7
00:00:36.083 --> 00:00:38.916
[Toru whimpering]

8
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.916
-[rain pouring on live stream]
-[boy] What. what do you want?

9
00:00:44.625 --> 00:00:46.166
-[blows thudding]
-[boy] Hey! [groans]

10
00:00:46.250 --> 00:00:49.041
Like a savior. a hero appeared
out of nowhere.

11
00:00:49.125 --> 00:00:51.583
-[boy yelping. groaning]
-[Shimura] And saved me.

12
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:54.125
[boys yelping. groaning]

13
00:00:54.208 --> 00:00:55.708
Why are you here?

14
00:00:55.791 --> 00:00:57.208
[boys groaning] Ah!

15
00:00:57.708 --> 00:00:59.125
[music intensifies]

16
00:00:59.208 --> 00:01:01.583
[boy groaning. coughing]

17
00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:06.416
[music stops]

18
00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:07.625
Let's go.

19
00:01:07.708 --> 00:01:09.333
[boys coughing. grunting]

20
00:01:13.916 --> 00:01:15.708
[Shimura] And this hero

21
00:01:16.625 --> 00:01:19.958
was insanely strong… and cool.

22
00:01:21.666 --> 00:01:22.666
[laughs softly]

23
00:01:22.750 --> 00:01:27.583
[whimpering]

24
00:01:31.750 --> 00:01:33.500
Asamiya. you okay?

25
00:01:33.583 --> 00:01:35.708
Yeah. I'm just fine.

26
00:01:37.166 --> 00:01:41.208
[Shimura] But truthfully…
I couldn't help myself.

27
00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:47.125
I couldn't help but resent this hero.

28
00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:51.750
[thunder rumbling]

29
00:01:51.833 --> 00:01:52.916
Let's go.

30
00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.000
[gentle music playing]

31
00:01:57.875 --> 00:01:59.750
But shortly afterwards.

32
00:02:00.750 --> 00:02:03.416
a feeling of loathing overcame me.

33
00:02:04.375 --> 00:02:06.041
for feeling this way.

34
00:02:10.875 --> 00:02:12.291
Oh. Shimura.

35
00:02:29.833 --> 00:02:32.375
[sobbing]

36
00:02:32.958 --> 00:02:35.708
[Shimura] The nightmare
finally came to an end.

37
00:02:35.791 --> 00:02:37.750
[thunder rumbling]

38
00:02:40.125 --> 00:02:41.625
And so did…

39
00:02:43.333 --> 00:02:44.541
my life.

40
00:02:46.666 --> 00:02:52.458
VIRAL HIT

41
00:02:55.166 --> 00:02:56.125
WHAT'S THIS?

42
00:02:56.208 --> 00:02:57.666
IS HE BACK FOR REAL?!

43
00:02:57.750 --> 00:02:58.750
LONG OVERDUE!

44
00:02:58.833 --> 00:03:00.625
[Hamaken] Sorry to keep you waiting.

45
00:03:00.708 --> 00:03:04.291
Hamaken TV is relaunching itself.

46
00:03:04.375 --> 00:03:08.416
From now on. there will be
no more here's Mr Nice Guy. you see?

47
00:03:08.500 --> 00:03:12.208
Hey! You better get yourself ready for it.

48
00:03:12.291 --> 00:03:13.666
SCUMBAG ACTIVATED LOL

49
00:03:13.750 --> 00:03:14.750
LOVE THIS VERSION

50
00:03:14.833 --> 00:03:17.333
I even brought a guest for you today.

51
00:03:17.416 --> 00:03:20.541
We've had him made up nicely.
It wasn't easy!

52
00:03:20.625 --> 00:03:22.458
Yeah! That's why I said
that I would do it.

53
00:03:22.541 --> 00:03:23.375
POOR GUY LOL

54
00:03:24.041 --> 00:03:25.583
Hey.

55
00:03:26.708 --> 00:03:30.458
Is it true that you're
the editor for Viral Hit? Yeah?

56
00:03:30.541 --> 00:03:31.625
[giggles]

57
00:03:31.708 --> 00:03:33.958
What? You didn't have
any friends in real life.

58
00:03:34.041 --> 00:03:35.708
so you turned to the Internet?

59
00:03:35.791 --> 00:03:37.250
What a loser! [giggles]

60
00:03:37.333 --> 00:03:39.500
-Are you listening?
-[pensive music playing]

61
00:03:39.583 --> 00:03:41.791
[girl 1] She asked if you could hear us.

62
00:03:42.375 --> 00:03:44.416
[girl 2] Wait. She's serious?

63
00:03:44.500 --> 00:03:47.083
[girl 3] What's with her?
She's got problems.

64
00:03:47.166 --> 00:03:48.500
[girl 1 scoffs] Freak.

65
00:03:48.583 --> 00:03:51.125
Rest in peace. Shimura.

66
00:03:51.208 --> 00:03:53.291
-Oh. come back!
-[boy 1] We'll miss you!

67
00:03:53.375 --> 00:03:54.833
[boys laughing]

68
00:03:54.916 --> 00:03:55.833
Edit these for me.

69
00:03:55.916 --> 00:03:57.416
I want them done by lunch.

70
00:03:58.083 --> 00:03:59.583
Uh. hang on though--

71
00:03:59.666 --> 00:04:00.833
[loud slam]

72
00:04:03.375 --> 00:04:04.416
[groans]

73
00:04:04.500 --> 00:04:06.166
You'll do it. won't you?

74
00:04:07.125 --> 00:04:08.250
[splutters] Of course.

75
00:04:08.333 --> 00:04:11.375
Just leave it to me.
I'll get on it now. Yes.

76
00:04:12.666 --> 00:04:14.250
[pensive music continues]

77
00:04:14.333 --> 00:04:16.083
VIRAL HIT'S GONE FOR GOOD

78
00:04:16.166 --> 00:04:18.166
SHIMURA. YOU STILL ALIVE? LOL

79
00:04:18.250 --> 00:04:20.083
THIS CHANNEL IS DEAD LOLOL

80
00:04:22.041 --> 00:04:23.625
They're all idiots.

81
00:04:24.875 --> 00:04:26.416
ARE YOU OKAY?
I'M WORRIED.

82
00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:27.500
PLEASE REPLY

83
00:04:27.583 --> 00:04:29.583
[indistinct chatter]

84
00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:34.458
Shimura flaked on us.
Asamiya. you know why?

85
00:04:34.541 --> 00:04:37.416
Ah. it's. uh. possible
he's not feeling well.

86
00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:38.958
Oh. I know why he's away.

87
00:04:39.041 --> 00:04:41.083
-Wait. what?
-Look what I found yesterday.

88
00:04:41.833 --> 00:04:44.291
-[man 1] Wait. is that Shimura?
-[laughter on video]

89
00:04:44.375 --> 00:04:45.333
Man. that's brutal.

90
00:04:45.416 --> 00:04:46.625
[man 2 laughing]

91
00:04:46.708 --> 00:04:49.750
Asamiya. don't tell me
that's your voice in the video.

92
00:04:50.375 --> 00:04:51.500
Oh. definitely not.

93
00:04:51.583 --> 00:04:53.000
[man 2] I think it is.

94
00:04:53.083 --> 00:04:55.375
I'd rather be dead than be seen like that.

95
00:04:56.125 --> 00:04:58.708
[man 1] I'd be so embarrassed.
I'd never leave home.

96
00:04:58.791 --> 00:05:01.000
[laughs] Naked on the ground is
the ultimate humiliation.

97
00:05:01.083 --> 00:05:03.458
-[man 1] Yeah. tell me about it.
-[man 2 laughing]

98
00:05:03.541 --> 00:05:05.708
I think the two of you are very cruel.

99
00:05:06.625 --> 00:05:07.875
[man 2] What?

100
00:05:07.958 --> 00:05:10.041
No. just forget it.

101
00:05:10.708 --> 00:05:11.875
Yeah.

102
00:05:12.583 --> 00:05:14.208
I don't think he came to school.

103
00:05:15.125 --> 00:05:16.375
Oh dear.

104
00:05:16.958 --> 00:05:18.958
I'm worried about his injuries.

105
00:05:19.041 --> 00:05:20.458
[Ogi] He's probably fine.

106
00:05:20.958 --> 00:05:22.166
What worries me

107
00:05:23.166 --> 00:05:24.916
is that he lost his dignity.

108
00:05:26.666 --> 00:05:29.000
That's one thing we can't help him with.

109
00:05:35.708 --> 00:05:39.041
-[pop music playing over speakers]
-Huh? Oh. you bought the mascara?

110
00:05:39.125 --> 00:05:42.291
I recommend it.
I want everyone to try it out.

111
00:05:43.333 --> 00:05:44.208
HOW'S SHIMURA?

112
00:05:44.291 --> 00:05:45.708
IS VIRAL HIT OVER?

113
00:05:45.791 --> 00:05:46.750
HE WAS TOO COCKY

114
00:05:46.833 --> 00:05:48.500
Viral Hit?

115
00:05:49.291 --> 00:05:50.125
Shimura?

116
00:05:50.208 --> 00:05:51.916
IS SHIMURA COMING TO SCHOOL??

117
00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.125
DO A COLLAB PLZ LOL

118
00:05:53.208 --> 00:05:54.375
Oh. you guys!

119
00:05:54.458 --> 00:05:57.208
All of this "Shimura. Shimura."
it's annoying.

120
00:05:57.291 --> 00:05:59.666
Forget about him. It's all over.

121
00:06:02.083 --> 00:06:04.083
[birds twittering]

122
00:06:12.583 --> 00:06:14.041
[doorbell buzzing]

123
00:06:17.416 --> 00:06:19.583
[doorbell buzzing]

124
00:06:36.250 --> 00:06:38.375
Nice to meet you… I guess.

125
00:06:44.458 --> 00:06:45.500
[Kaho] I see.

126
00:06:46.291 --> 00:06:48.458
It's good you're worried about him too.

127
00:06:49.416 --> 00:06:51.875
[Aki] I feel like I'm partially to blame.

128
00:06:51.958 --> 00:06:53.583
[Kaho] Maybe we both are.

129
00:06:54.083 --> 00:06:56.833
[Aki] What do you mean?
All you did was go on a date with him.

130
00:06:56.916 --> 00:06:57.750
[Kaho] What?

131
00:06:57.833 --> 00:07:00.208
[Kaho] I… I mean. it wasn't really a date.

132
00:07:03.625 --> 00:07:08.791
If he runs away now… then he'll
spend the rest of his life running.

133
00:07:10.125 --> 00:07:12.625
-And that worries me.
-Why's that?

134
00:07:14.208 --> 00:07:18.250
I think that… his life. it has a value.

135
00:07:19.041 --> 00:07:21.875
Were you… a part of his team?

136
00:07:23.208 --> 00:07:25.083
Yes. sort of. I guess.

137
00:07:26.500 --> 00:07:27.500
I see.

138
00:07:29.625 --> 00:07:33.458
I wish… I knew where he was. that's all.

139
00:07:34.375 --> 00:07:35.750
Sorry to take up your time.

140
00:07:35.833 --> 00:07:38.166
[sighs] Mm. It's good we talked.

141
00:07:38.666 --> 00:07:39.666
Take care.

142
00:07:46.583 --> 00:07:48.708
I guess we're all alike.

143
00:07:50.541 --> 00:07:52.458
Hamaken TV!

144
00:07:52.541 --> 00:07:53.666
INSTANT MENACE LOL

145
00:07:53.708 --> 00:07:57.500
Today. I'll have Kanegon who knows
Shimura pretty well now. I think.

146
00:07:57.583 --> 00:07:59.583
Tell us the true story about Viral Hit.

147
00:07:59.666 --> 00:08:00.750
Huh?

148
00:08:00.833 --> 00:08:01.750
[boys laugh]

149
00:08:01.833 --> 00:08:03.000
[grunts]

150
00:08:03.083 --> 00:08:05.291
-[boy 1] Ready?
-[boy 2] Okay. we're set.

151
00:08:05.375 --> 00:08:09.041
You be completely honest now.
What was Shimura like?

152
00:08:09.125 --> 00:08:11.541
Uh… He. uh…

153
00:08:12.333 --> 00:08:15.583
-Shi… Shimura was--
-Shimura was what? Tell us. Come on.

154
00:08:18.833 --> 00:08:21.166
Shi… Shimura was…

155
00:08:21.666 --> 00:08:23.958
Let's take over the world
with this channel.

156
00:08:24.041 --> 00:08:25.708
You did it. Shimura!

157
00:08:26.208 --> 00:08:29.166
[Shimura] Thank you!
You helped me get my senses!

158
00:08:29.250 --> 00:08:32.916
Today we become known as Viral Hit!

159
00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:35.500
[breathing heavily]]

160
00:08:36.083 --> 00:08:38.583
R… really.

161
00:08:39.583 --> 00:08:41.000
He was a hideous guy.

162
00:08:41.083 --> 00:08:43.500
[straining] Oh! Oh! Was he now?

163
00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:46.375
-He was all about--
-Yeah? What?

164
00:08:46.458 --> 00:08:49.833
All he cared about was going viral
and getting donations.

165
00:08:49.916 --> 00:08:53.583
Ah. yes! And that's why he lied
and accused me of being a fraud!

166
00:08:53.666 --> 00:08:54.916
Uh-huh.

167
00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:57.833
And he staged
all those fight videos. didn't he?

168
00:08:58.333 --> 00:09:02.791
Yeah. he did. That guy will do
anything for money.

169
00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:06.250
But wait.
You're friends with him. aren't you?

170
00:09:06.333 --> 00:09:07.708
What are you talking about?

171
00:09:07.791 --> 00:09:11.000
Why would I want to be
friends with that loser?

172
00:09:11.583 --> 00:09:14.916
I don't ever… wanna see him again.

173
00:09:15.708 --> 00:09:18.208
You heard it. You guys get it now?

174
00:09:18.750 --> 00:09:22.541
The next video is going to be
where Shimura apologizes

175
00:09:22.625 --> 00:09:24.875
for tricking you
into thinking he's a hero.

176
00:09:24.958 --> 00:09:27.500
You'll love it!

177
00:09:27.583 --> 00:09:29.416
Okay!

178
00:09:29.500 --> 00:09:31.958
-This is seriously blowing up.
-[Hamaken] This is great content.

179
00:09:32.041 --> 00:09:33.166
HAMAKEN'S GETTING REVENGE

180
00:09:33.250 --> 00:09:35.583
Seems I'm a better producer than you. huh?

181
00:09:35.666 --> 00:09:37.291
Yeah. you definitely are.

182
00:09:37.375 --> 00:09:39.750
-Where is Shimura now?
-[whimpering]

183
00:09:39.833 --> 00:09:41.416
[Toru] Ow! You're hurting me!

184
00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:43.291
How long is he going to be
skipping school for?

185
00:09:43.375 --> 00:09:45.541
-I don't know--
-Tell me the truth! I wanna know.

186
00:09:45.625 --> 00:09:46.666
You bring him to me.

187
00:09:46.750 --> 00:09:49.708
I told you! I don't have
anything to do with him anymore!

188
00:09:49.791 --> 00:09:52.208
You're lying. aren't you? Aren't you?!

189
00:09:52.291 --> 00:09:55.166
Who would ever believe
what you're saying. hey? Hey?

190
00:09:55.250 --> 00:09:57.541
Do you have any idea
what you've done to me?

191
00:09:58.041 --> 00:10:01.458
You go get him and drag his ass back here.
You understand?

192
00:10:01.541 --> 00:10:02.708
[Toru] Okay. I will.

193
00:10:02.791 --> 00:10:05.916
I promise. I will.
I'll do it. I'll do it.

194
00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:06.875
[Toru straining]

195
00:10:07.791 --> 00:10:09.625
[gags. shudders]

196
00:10:16.708 --> 00:10:17.541
[Aki] Hey!

197
00:10:17.625 --> 00:10:19.625
[indistinct chatter]

198
00:10:22.958 --> 00:10:24.541
How's he holding up?

199
00:10:25.250 --> 00:10:27.125
-Whoa!
-How the hell should I know?

200
00:10:27.208 --> 00:10:29.041
Why does everyone keep asking me that?

201
00:10:33.583 --> 00:10:35.166
This is all his fault.

202
00:10:36.708 --> 00:10:38.291
He brought it on.

203
00:10:39.875 --> 00:10:42.291
-He needs to come back to school--
-Where are you going?

204
00:10:42.375 --> 00:10:44.791
The hospital! I need to find where he is.

205
00:10:44.875 --> 00:10:46.250
The hospital?

206
00:10:48.416 --> 00:10:50.125
It's where she is.

207
00:10:51.708 --> 00:10:53.000
His mother.

208
00:10:56.500 --> 00:10:59.333
[footsteps departing]

209
00:11:01.541 --> 00:11:03.000
[nurse] Is that for your son?

210
00:11:03.083 --> 00:11:04.166
Mm-hmm.

211
00:11:05.208 --> 00:11:09.166
If I wasn't so sick.
I'd be able to do this so quickly.

212
00:11:09.666 --> 00:11:12.666
Ah. don't push
yourself too hard. Mrs. Shimura.

213
00:11:14.458 --> 00:11:16.416
Oh! Are you visiting someone?

214
00:11:16.500 --> 00:11:18.666
Uh. yeah. Yeah. that's right.

215
00:11:23.916 --> 00:11:25.125
Hello.

216
00:11:25.208 --> 00:11:28.916
Uh. do… do you happen to know
where Shimura is?

217
00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.250
I can't find him anywhere.

218
00:11:31.416 --> 00:11:32.625
You need him?

219
00:11:33.958 --> 00:11:37.375
Oh. So sorry you came all this way.

220
00:11:37.916 --> 00:11:40.125
He hasn't visited me in a few days.

221
00:11:41.166 --> 00:11:43.000
Apparently. he's busy.

222
00:11:43.541 --> 00:11:46.083
Oh. I see. I understand.

223
00:11:47.250 --> 00:11:48.291
Are you…

224
00:11:49.875 --> 00:11:50.791
Kaneko?

225
00:11:51.708 --> 00:11:52.666
Uh…

226
00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:56.000
-Yes.
-Oh. that's great!

227
00:11:57.041 --> 00:12:00.958
He told me about you
with a big smile on his face.

228
00:12:01.541 --> 00:12:03.833
He said you were
his first friend in class.

229
00:12:05.541 --> 00:12:09.375
Thanks to you.
he actually enjoys going to school.

230
00:12:10.916 --> 00:12:13.875
-I'm like this. you know. [chuckles]
-[tender music playing]

231
00:12:13.958 --> 00:12:16.208
I put a lot of burden on him.

232
00:12:16.708 --> 00:12:19.833
I was worried
he wasn't having fun at school.

233
00:12:23.291 --> 00:12:27.041
Thank you for being there for him.
His first friend.

234
00:12:31.041 --> 00:12:31.958
Yeah.

235
00:12:35.958 --> 00:12:37.958
[cries softly]

236
00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.250
[firmly] Excuse me.

237
00:12:51.500 --> 00:12:53.500
[music fades]

238
00:13:13.041 --> 00:13:14.916
Go on! Jump then!

239
00:13:17.875 --> 00:13:18.916
It'll hurt

240
00:13:19.958 --> 00:13:22.125
a lot more than the punches you took.

241
00:13:24.041 --> 00:13:25.250
Leave me alone.

242
00:13:27.333 --> 00:13:28.500
My life…

243
00:13:30.916 --> 00:13:32.833
it's all over now.

244
00:13:34.666 --> 00:13:37.250
You saw how I embarrassed myself.

245
00:13:39.416 --> 00:13:41.833
There's no point continuing on.

246
00:13:43.583 --> 00:13:44.916
I'm better off

247
00:13:45.416 --> 00:13:46.750
being dead.

248
00:13:49.791 --> 00:13:52.083
[dreamy music playing]

249
00:14:04.458 --> 00:14:05.333
[gasps]

250
00:14:07.708 --> 00:14:08.708
Huh?

251
00:14:13.625 --> 00:14:14.791
Uh…

252
00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:20.166
They're all waiting for you. you know.

253
00:14:21.916 --> 00:14:24.916
Viral Hit subscriber numbers
are increasing. even now.

254
00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.916
[poignant music playing]

255
00:14:27.000 --> 00:14:28.000
Who cares?!

256
00:14:30.208 --> 00:14:33.375
The next video will draw
a huge viewership.

257
00:14:33.458 --> 00:14:36.416
-I don't care about that!
-This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity!

258
00:14:36.500 --> 00:14:38.750
That's enough! Leave me alone now!

259
00:14:41.625 --> 00:14:43.333
Okay. [sniffs]

260
00:14:43.875 --> 00:14:44.750
