Far out.

525
00:28:20.583 --> 00:28:22.208
[Shimura crying]

526
00:28:32.291 --> 00:28:34.291
[sobbing]

527
00:28:34.375 --> 00:28:35.250
[sniffing]

528
00:28:42.083 --> 00:28:44.000
[voice breaking] You did real good.

529
00:28:49.833 --> 00:28:51.458
So don't cry anymore.

530
00:28:54.583 --> 00:28:56.875
[crying]

531
00:28:58.916 --> 00:28:59.958
Shimura.

532
00:29:02.541 --> 00:29:03.500
LEGENDARY

533
00:29:03.583 --> 00:29:04.791
SHIMURA'S THE MAN

534
00:29:06.250 --> 00:29:07.916
That was a beautiful win.

535
00:29:08.000 --> 00:29:09.916
[gentle classical music continues]

536
00:29:10.000 --> 00:29:11.083
[laughs]

537
00:29:11.625 --> 00:29:12.875
[sniffles]

538
00:29:12.958 --> 00:29:13.875
[sighs]

539
00:29:25.791 --> 00:29:26.791
Shimura.

540
00:29:27.833 --> 00:29:29.291
I want to thank you.

541
00:29:34.333 --> 00:29:35.708
So. thank you.

542
00:29:40.333 --> 00:29:41.458
What does it say?

543
00:29:41.541 --> 00:29:42.375
Huh?

544
00:29:43.166 --> 00:29:44.333
Double?

545
00:29:44.416 --> 00:29:46.916
We've already hit 700.000.

546
00:29:47.416 --> 00:29:50.333
It's only a matter of time
before we hit one million!

547
00:29:50.416 --> 00:29:52.541
-[Shimura] What about the donations?
-Hey.

548
00:29:52.625 --> 00:29:55.250
-Let's see. It's past a million yen!
-[joyful music playing]

549
00:29:55.333 --> 00:30:00.541
Uh. then it's… then our share.
it's more than 600.000 yen!

550
00:30:00.625 --> 00:30:03.333
I thought you did it to save me.

551
00:30:03.416 --> 00:30:06.125
Why would I?
This was all about money. No more.

552
00:30:07.166 --> 00:30:10.000
You bastard. I got all emotional.

553
00:30:10.083 --> 00:30:11.666
-I thought you came for me!
-Oh.

554
00:30:11.750 --> 00:30:15.333
But aren't you the one who said
that I'd do anything for money?

555
00:30:15.416 --> 00:30:16.416
You were watching?

556
00:30:17.458 --> 00:30:19.916
Sure did. I'm a hideous guy.

557
00:30:20.500 --> 00:30:23.000
No wonder you don't have friends!
You're mean. ya know?

558
00:30:23.083 --> 00:30:24.000
Say what you want.

559
00:30:24.083 --> 00:30:26.791
It can hardly hurt
coming from a guy like you.

560
00:30:26.875 --> 00:30:28.625
-What do you mean by that?
-Ah!

561
00:30:29.333 --> 00:30:30.833
You want to fight?

562
00:30:30.916 --> 00:30:32.166
I'll take you on.

563
00:30:33.041 --> 00:30:33.916
[Toru grunts]

564
00:30:34.000 --> 00:30:36.125
-[Shimura] Don't copy me.
-[Toru] Shut up!

565
00:30:36.208 --> 00:30:38.541
[Toru straining. grunting]

566
00:30:38.625 --> 00:30:41.125
[both grunting. laughing]

567
00:30:41.208 --> 00:30:42.291
[Shimura] Whoa!

568
00:30:44.125 --> 00:30:46.166
Ah! [laughs]

569
00:30:48.916 --> 00:30:51.666
[grunting. laughing]

570
00:30:51.750 --> 00:30:52.791
[music fades]

571
00:30:52.875 --> 00:30:53.750
[Toru screams]

572
00:30:54.583 --> 00:30:55.458
[Shimura] Ah!

573
00:30:55.958 --> 00:30:58.166
[indistinct chatter]

574
00:30:58.250 --> 00:31:00.708
-[boy 1] I hope he comes today.
-[boy 2] Seriously. yesterday--

575
00:31:00.791 --> 00:31:02.416
-[boy 3] Hey. Shimura!
-Oh. Shimura!

576
00:31:02.500 --> 00:31:04.333
Oh. it's Shimura! [laughs]

577
00:31:04.416 --> 00:31:06.083
[boy 1] You were incredible.

578
00:31:07.041 --> 00:31:09.708
[Shimura] Hamaken hasn't come to school
since that day.

579
00:31:09.791 --> 00:31:11.291
[boy 3] It's all thanks to you!

580
00:31:11.375 --> 00:31:14.333
[Shimura] I know what he's afraid of
isn't silly old me.

581
00:31:14.416 --> 00:31:15.500
[boy 2] Me too!

582
00:31:16.208 --> 00:31:18.291
[Shimura] It's the reality
that he's hit rock bottom.

583
00:31:18.916 --> 00:31:20.500
So crazy!

584
00:31:20.583 --> 00:31:23.625
[boy 1] I'm really sorry
I never tried to intervene.

585
00:31:24.291 --> 00:31:26.333
There's nothing… you could have done.

586
00:31:26.416 --> 00:31:28.000
-[all chuckle. gasp]
-You're such a saint!

587
00:31:28.083 --> 00:31:30.958
[Shimura] I imagine
Hamaken's suffering and…

588
00:31:32.833 --> 00:31:35.333
Oh. it serves him right! He deserves it!

589
00:31:35.416 --> 00:31:37.458
[Toru] Okay! Hi! Hi!

590
00:31:37.541 --> 00:31:40.000
Do you all get what we can do now? Do you?

591
00:31:40.083 --> 00:31:41.916
Hey? It's all because of me.

592
00:31:42.000 --> 00:31:44.375
the producer and creator
of this great channel--

593
00:31:44.458 --> 00:31:46.500
Shimura. want to go to karaoke sometime?

594
00:31:46.583 --> 00:31:48.291
[Shimura] Huh? Oh. uh…

595
00:31:48.375 --> 00:31:50.333
-Mm. yeah. sure. if I'm free.
-[boys chuckle]

596
00:31:50.416 --> 00:31:51.958
-[boy 2] Yay!
-[boy 1] That's so good.

597
00:31:52.041 --> 00:31:54.041
[boy 3] We're gonna have
the best time with Shimura!

598
00:31:54.125 --> 00:31:55.583
[boys laughing. chattering]

599
00:31:55.666 --> 00:31:56.541
[music ends]

600
00:31:57.625 --> 00:32:00.000
-[girl 1 laughs] What? So lame!
-[girl 2] Isn't she cringe?

601
00:32:00.083 --> 00:32:01.375
[girl 3] Is she for real?

602
00:32:01.458 --> 00:32:04.875
[girl 4 laughs] They're dissing her.
saying she's Hamaken's girl.

603
00:32:04.958 --> 00:32:06.416
-Not even good.
-[girl 5] Seriously.

604
00:32:06.500 --> 00:32:07.500
[loud slam]

605
00:32:09.083 --> 00:32:11.125
-Let's go to the bathroom.
-[Girl 4] Let's go.

606
00:32:11.625 --> 00:32:13.000
[girl 5 laughs]

607
00:32:13.083 --> 00:32:14.416
[phone buzzing]

608
00:32:14.500 --> 00:32:16.500
[indistinct chattering]

609
00:32:17.250 --> 00:32:18.750
NEW MESSAGE

610
00:32:19.666 --> 00:32:22.833
INVITATION TO PARTNER
AS AN OFFICIAL INFLUENCER

611
00:32:24.958 --> 00:32:26.375
[students laugh]

612
00:32:27.291 --> 00:32:28.458
What are you doing?

613
00:32:29.125 --> 00:32:30.333
Oh. Aki.

614
00:32:30.416 --> 00:32:31.708
Where's Shimura?

615
00:32:32.666 --> 00:32:33.625
How would I know?

616
00:32:36.875 --> 00:32:37.791
What's wrong?

617
00:32:43.208 --> 00:32:45.125
So he's amazing. I get it.

618
00:32:46.458 --> 00:32:47.458
I really do.

619
00:32:48.875 --> 00:32:51.000
-Oh. you're jealous.
-I wouldn't call it jealousy.

620
00:32:51.083 --> 00:32:53.583
-Jealous men don't get the girls.
-I just said I'm not jealous!

621
00:32:57.166 --> 00:33:01.583
You know your job now…
is to find his next opponent.

622
00:33:05.375 --> 00:33:07.166
I have high hopes for you.

623
00:33:08.625 --> 00:33:09.625
Huh?

624
00:33:13.416 --> 00:33:14.916
High hopes?

625
00:33:17.125 --> 00:33:18.125
You do?

626
00:33:19.416 --> 00:33:20.708
CEO

627
00:33:20.750 --> 00:33:22.541
As I mentioned in my DM.

628
00:33:22.625 --> 00:33:25.791
we will be honored to have you join
our influencer agency. Rumi.

629
00:33:26.833 --> 00:33:28.958
We are part of BAD FELLOWS Group.

630
00:33:29.041 --> 00:33:33.250
We can get you gigs and anything
you can think of. like reality shows.

631
00:33:33.333 --> 00:33:35.833
Once you get more exposure
and become more well-known--

632
00:33:35.916 --> 00:33:36.791
Will you

633
00:33:37.875 --> 00:33:39.416
help me get more followers?

634
00:33:39.500 --> 00:33:42.083
[light piano music playing]

635
00:33:42.166 --> 00:33:44.625
-I want more followers.
-[chuckles]

636
00:33:46.458 --> 00:33:49.666
Of course. If you let me handle it.

637
00:33:51.666 --> 00:33:53.208
Are you free after this?

638
00:33:56.458 --> 00:33:59.833
['50s rock music playing]

639
00:33:59.916 --> 00:34:01.625
[Shimura] I caused you so much trouble.

640
00:34:01.708 --> 00:34:03.083
I'm terribly sorry.

641
00:34:04.125 --> 00:34:05.083
[clears throat]

642
00:34:06.791 --> 00:34:08.333
-[bell jangles]
-I'm terribly sorry--

643
00:34:08.416 --> 00:34:10.500
-[both yell]
-[clattering]

644
00:34:10.583 --> 00:34:12.750
-[Shimura] Ah. sorry about that.
-[Kaho] So sorry.

645
00:34:13.250 --> 00:34:14.708
I'm sorry. I didn't see you coming.

646
00:34:14.791 --> 00:34:16.625
Oh no. that was completely my fault.

647
00:34:16.708 --> 00:34:17.541
[Kaho exhales]

648
00:34:18.291 --> 00:34:19.666
Here. Use this.

649
00:34:19.750 --> 00:34:21.500
Oh. thank you.

650
00:34:22.500 --> 00:34:23.416
It's been a while.

651
00:34:24.583 --> 00:34:27.083
-[gentle electronic music playing]
-Mm. Yes. it has.

652
00:34:27.166 --> 00:34:28.416
[Kaho laughs]

653
00:34:30.416 --> 00:34:34.916
I'm very sorry… for putting you
through so much worry.

654
00:34:35.583 --> 00:34:41.083
I knew that you were trying to contact me.
but after you saw me like that. I…

655
00:34:43.458 --> 00:34:44.291
Thank you.

656
00:34:45.666 --> 00:34:46.875
Uh…

657
00:34:46.958 --> 00:34:49.416
You were trying
to protect me again. weren't you?

658
00:34:52.875 --> 00:34:55.916
It's all right.
You've already saved me enough.

659
00:34:57.333 --> 00:34:58.166
I don't think so.

660
00:34:58.375 --> 00:35:02.083
So it's my turn. now.
I can save you!

661
00:35:02.166 --> 00:35:03.416
[both laugh]

662
00:35:03.500 --> 00:35:04.666
That's silly.

663
00:35:09.333 --> 00:35:10.500
Uh. well…

664
00:35:12.208 --> 00:35:15.541
Would you like to go
to a café with me again?

665
00:35:16.041 --> 00:35:17.500
Next time. it's on me.

666
00:35:17.583 --> 00:35:18.875
Would I? Yes!

667
00:35:18.958 --> 00:35:21.250
-Oh. yay!
-[giggles]

668
00:35:21.333 --> 00:35:22.500
Then it's a date.

669
00:35:22.583 --> 00:35:23.541
Mm. a date.

670
00:35:23.625 --> 00:35:26.208
-See you.
-Mm. Yeah. Bye for now.

671
00:35:39.000 --> 00:35:40.666
[music fades]

672
00:35:40.750 --> 00:35:41.833
[gasps] Oh!

673
00:35:45.333 --> 00:35:46.291
Oh.

674
00:36:04.500 --> 00:36:06.458
Welcome home. Asamiya.

675
00:36:06.541 --> 00:36:08.000
Yes. thank you.

676
00:36:13.250 --> 00:36:17.541
[ominous music playing]

677
00:36:26.708 --> 00:36:28.166
Anything to report?

678
00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:31.250
I just spent a little time with Tatsuya.

679
00:36:31.333 --> 00:36:32.416
And. why?

680
00:36:32.875 --> 00:36:36.250
-We talked about the entrance exam--
-Exactly how long were you with him?

681
00:36:36.333 --> 00:36:37.291
Two hours.

682
00:36:38.333 --> 00:36:40.083
He's a fighter. is he not?

683
00:36:41.166 --> 00:36:44.500
Will someone like that be
beneficial to your future. Asamiya?

684
00:36:45.666 --> 00:36:48.958
Don't waste your time like this.
You must focus on your studies.

685
00:36:50.458 --> 00:36:51.291
Hmm.

686
00:36:52.791 --> 00:36:53.791
Thank you for the meal--

687
00:36:53.875 --> 00:36:56.083
You haven't been seeing
anyone else. have you?

688
00:36:56.166 --> 00:36:58.166
[ominous music builds]

689
00:36:58.250 --> 00:36:59.541
No. I haven't.

690
00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:04.291
[moaning]

691
00:37:06.125 --> 00:37:07.166
[Eiji] Rumi.

692
00:37:07.250 --> 00:37:08.125
[moans]

693
00:37:08.666 --> 00:37:09.750
You're great.

694
00:37:10.625 --> 00:37:12.916
[moaning continues]

695
00:37:17.500 --> 00:37:19.708
Whoa! 560.000!

696
00:37:19.791 --> 00:37:22.166
[Toru] Can you believe it?
Our channel's blowing up!

697
00:37:22.833 --> 00:37:25.958
This is all thanks to my producing skills.

698
00:37:26.541 --> 00:37:27.541
Look at this.

699
00:37:29.625 --> 00:37:30.833
[Aki] That's BAD FELLOWS.

700
00:37:30.916 --> 00:37:32.833
-Who are they?
-You don't know?

701
00:37:32.916 --> 00:37:37.166
It's a super popular show that pits
amateur fighters against each other.

702
00:37:37.250 --> 00:37:39.583
The CEO hit the jackpot with this.

703
00:37:39.666 --> 00:37:42.750
Now. he's expanding
into the entertainment industry.

704
00:37:42.833 --> 00:37:44.375
[Shimura] Mmm.

705
00:37:46.708 --> 00:37:48.125
Read the comments.

706
00:37:49.708 --> 00:37:50.708
IT LOOKS STAGED

707
00:37:50.791 --> 00:37:52.541
I PREFER VIRAL HIT

708
00:37:52.625 --> 00:37:54.125
VIRAL HIT IS LEGIT

709
00:37:55.041 --> 00:37:58.083
Viral Hit's channel…
it's competing with them.

710
00:37:58.166 --> 00:37:59.666
This affects us how?

711
00:37:59.750 --> 00:38:03.833
My point is. what we offer is
the real deal. It's legit.

712
00:38:03.916 --> 00:38:04.833
VIRAL HIT IS LEGIT

713
00:38:04.916 --> 00:38:06.125
Of course. And?

714
00:38:06.208 --> 00:38:08.666
I have the next opponent lined up for you.

715
00:38:09.458 --> 00:38:11.791
You see how I'm a genius producer?

716
00:38:11.875 --> 00:38:15.791
[jaunty music playing]

717
00:38:15.875 --> 00:38:18.250
[all grunting]

718
00:38:22.166 --> 00:38:23.125
Let's go.

719
00:38:23.625 --> 00:38:24.916
What do you mean? Wait. why?

720
00:38:25.000 --> 00:38:27.666
This is crazy.
What about the weight difference?

721
00:38:27.750 --> 00:38:30.166
Yeah. sure… but it'll be a great visual.

722
00:38:30.250 --> 00:38:32.416
I've got an idea.
Why don't you fight them?

723
00:38:32.500 --> 00:38:34.083
See how safe you feel.

724
00:38:34.166 --> 00:38:35.166
Huh?

725
00:38:35.250 --> 00:38:36.375
-[loud slam]
-[men grunting]

726
00:38:36.458 --> 00:38:37.708
[jaunty music continues]

727
00:38:37.791 --> 00:38:39.666
All right. get ready!

728
00:38:53.666 --> 00:38:54.833
Begin!

729
00:38:54.916 --> 00:38:55.916
-I give up!
-[music stops]

730
00:38:56.875 --> 00:38:58.416
[jaunty music resumes]

731
00:38:58.500 --> 00:39:01.541
So did you get a taste
of how it feels to fight? [chuckles]

732
00:39:01.625 --> 00:39:05.250
Assessing safety is an important part
of your work as a producer.

733
00:39:05.750 --> 00:39:07.916
Sure. but this
would have been spectacular.

734
00:39:08.000 --> 00:39:10.708
Next time book me a fighter on my level.

735
00:39:11.791 --> 00:39:13.791
You're both ganging up on me now.

736
00:39:15.166 --> 00:39:16.208
All right. then.

737
00:39:16.708 --> 00:39:18.416
Why don't you two do it yourself?

738
00:39:18.500 --> 00:39:20.875
Well. that's an idea.
We might just do that.

739
00:39:22.083 --> 00:39:23.166
Let's go.

740
00:39:23.250 --> 00:39:24.208
[Shimura] Mm.

741
00:39:25.125 --> 00:39:26.083
[music ends]

742
00:39:26.166 --> 00:39:27.375
They hate me.

743
00:39:29.666 --> 00:39:34.250
We need to develop a strategy
so we can figure out your next opponent.

744
00:39:34.333 --> 00:39:36.333
Be nice to do content other than fights.

745
00:39:36.416 --> 00:39:37.375
Mm.

746
00:39:37.875 --> 00:39:42.166
Oh. why don't you come to my place…
and we can brainstorm a bit.

747
00:39:42.833 --> 00:39:48.625
Oh. uh. my dad wouldn't…
like that much… since you live alone.

748
00:39:48.708 --> 00:39:50.166
You're right. yeah.

749
00:39:50.250 --> 00:39:52.541
I guess we'll need
to call off the meeting.

750
00:39:53.750 --> 00:39:54.833
Uh. no.

751
00:39:56.333 --> 00:39:59.333
We still need to discuss things.

752
00:40:00.291 --> 00:40:02.208
[pop music playing]

753
00:40:03.666 --> 00:40:06.208
FOLLOWERS 71.000

754
00:40:06.291 --> 00:40:07.250
♪ Uh-huh. uh-huh ♪

755
00:40:08.416 --> 00:40:10.416
[music subsides]

756
00:40:18.833 --> 00:40:20.916
Look. I already have
over 70.000 followers!

757
00:40:21.000 --> 00:40:22.541
RUMI
BEAUTY-LOVING HIGH SCHOOL GIRL (17)

758
00:40:22.625 --> 00:40:24.708
Rumi. you can aim much higher.

759
00:40:24.791 --> 00:40:27.541
Can I get to 600.000?
I want to shoot for more.

760
00:40:27.625 --> 00:40:30.375
Ha. Don't worry. I have a plan.

761
00:40:30.458 --> 00:40:31.958
-[Rumi] Mm.
-Come here.

762
00:40:34.125 --> 00:40:36.916
Rumi. you do know
I'll do anything for you.

763
00:40:37.000 --> 00:40:37.958
[chuckles]

764
00:40:39.791 --> 00:40:40.916
You know that.

765
00:40:41.916 --> 00:40:42.916
Mm-hmm.

766
00:40:43.583 --> 00:40:46.250
-[game music playing]
-[indistinct chatter]

767
00:40:46.333 --> 00:40:48.375
[game character] Don't listen to them!

768
00:40:49.250 --> 00:40:50.375
Kanegon.

769
00:40:51.083 --> 00:40:51.958
What do you want?

770
00:40:52.041 --> 00:40:53.458
What are you doing by yourself?

771
00:40:53.541 --> 00:40:54.583
You can't tell?

772
00:40:54.666 --> 00:40:56.500
What is it?  Are you guys fighting?

773
00:40:56.583 --> 00:40:57.625
Go away.

774
00:40:57.708 --> 00:41:00.500
[Rumi laughs] They're cruel to you.

775
00:41:01.166 --> 00:41:04.333
I actually appreciate how amazing you are.

776
00:41:09.916 --> 00:41:11.916
BARBER YASHIO

777
00:41:12.000 --> 00:41:15.083
[Aki humming]

778
00:41:29.958 --> 00:41:31.625
[dad humming]

779
00:41:33.666 --> 00:41:35.291
[Aki] You're in a very good mood today.

780
00:41:35.375 --> 00:41:36.500
Yeah.

781
00:41:36.583 --> 00:41:39.041
This is the first time
you've ever brought a friend here. hey?

782
00:41:39.458 --> 00:41:41.791
He's more like a… comrade.

783
00:41:41.875 --> 00:41:45.166
A comrade. So you made a friend.
That's the main thing.

784
00:41:45.250 --> 00:41:46.500
[Aki laughs]

785
00:41:46.583 --> 00:41:47.583
Hello?

786
00:41:48.083 --> 00:41:50.041
-Hi. come on in.
-You're late.

787
00:41:50.125 --> 00:41:51.541
-[Shimura] Sorry. I got lost.
-Mm?

788
00:41:51.625 --> 00:41:52.458
Let's get to it.

789
00:41:52.541 --> 00:41:53.583
Oh. yeah.

790
00:41:53.666 --> 00:41:55.541
I'm Shimura. sir.
We go to the same school.

791
00:41:55.625 --> 00:41:57.833
Oh. that's nice.

792
00:41:57.916 --> 00:42:00.083
Yes. so sorry to intrude.

793
00:42:00.166 --> 00:42:02.416
[footsteps departing]

794
00:42:02.500 --> 00:42:03.666
A boy?

795
00:42:04.875 --> 00:42:05.958
[dance music playing]

796
00:42:06.041 --> 00:42:08.041
[girls] Cheers! Cheers! Cheers!

797
00:42:08.125 --> 00:42:11.250
No way!
You're the one producing Viral Hit!

798
00:42:11.333 --> 00:42:12.291
It's nothing. really.

799
00:42:12.375 --> 00:42:15.333
Yes. I see all your videos
on Instagram too.

800
00:42:15.416 --> 00:42:17.125
Your channel's the talk of the town.

801
00:42:17.208 --> 00:42:18.041
-Oh. really?
-Mm-hmm!

802
00:42:18.125 --> 00:42:21.708
Well. people just don't get it.
The producer's role is the most important.

803
00:42:21.791 --> 00:42:23.166
Well. of course it is.

804
00:42:23.250 --> 00:42:25.875
It's the behind-the-scenes
that really counts.

805
00:42:25.958 --> 00:42:27.583
-Mature of you!
-[girl 1] Totally!

806
00:42:27.666 --> 00:42:28.625
-Totally.
-Totally.

807
00:42:28.708 --> 00:42:29.833
Oh. you think so?

808
00:42:29.916 --> 00:42:32.708
If it were me. I'd complain for sure.

809
00:42:32.791 --> 00:42:35.125
I'd say Viral Hit only got
this far because of me.

810
00:42:35.208 --> 00:42:36.375
Well. okay.

811
00:42:36.458 --> 00:42:40.125
I'm happy enough
as long as you're all happy! [chuckles]

812
00:42:40.208 --> 00:42:41.625
[all laughing]

813
00:42:41.708 --> 00:42:43.916
Ah. well. today's on me. so drink up!

814
00:42:44.000 --> 00:42:45.000
-Really?
-You sure?

815
00:42:45.083 --> 00:42:47.208
Well then. I won't hold back! Here.

816
00:42:47.291 --> 00:42:48.750
[all] Kanpai!

817
00:42:48.833 --> 00:42:50.333
[girl 1] Woo-hoo-hoo!

818
00:42:50.416 --> 00:42:53.416
[girls whooping. shouting]

819
00:42:53.500 --> 00:42:55.250
[girl 2] This is the life!

820
00:42:55.333 --> 00:42:56.250
[music stops]

821
00:42:57.666 --> 00:43:00.916
This is bad.
We didn't get a single donation.

822
00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:02.833
Not a single yen?

823
00:43:02.916 --> 00:43:05.750
This is the next opponent I'll fight!

824
00:43:06.916 --> 00:43:08.458
VIRAL HIT LIVE NOW

825
00:43:08.541 --> 00:43:10.791
[Aki] Looks like the viewers
didn't want that from you.

826
00:43:10.875 --> 00:43:12.166
FIGHT ALREADY

827
00:43:14.291 --> 00:43:18.000
-How much have we made so far?
-735.300.

828
00:43:18.666 --> 00:43:20.333
That's not enough.

829
00:43:20.458 --> 00:43:22.833
TOTAL AMOUNT DUE: 3.140.000 YEN

830
00:43:22.916 --> 00:43:26.041
So it has to be a fight.

831
00:43:28.916 --> 00:43:31.166
-[dance music playing
-Hey. Kaneko.

832
00:43:31.250 --> 00:43:32.333
Show us how you edit.

833
00:43:32.416 --> 00:43:33.666
-You really wanna know?
-Oh. yes!

834
00:43:33.750 --> 00:43:34.666
-Yes!
-Yes. please.

835
00:43:34.750 --> 00:43:36.291
Come on! Show them.

836
00:43:36.375 --> 00:43:38.083
-[girl 2] Yes.
-Really?

837
00:43:38.166 --> 00:43:39.916
Okay. [laughs]

838
00:43:40.000 --> 00:43:41.500
[girl 3] Oh. this is so great!

839
00:43:47.666 --> 00:43:50.208
-[music ends]
-Well. I should get going now.

840
00:43:50.291 --> 00:43:52.375
Oh. it's that late already.

841
00:43:53.583 --> 00:43:54.500
By the way...

842
00:43:55.541 --> 00:43:56.666
That video. I…

843
00:43:58.291 --> 00:43:59.375
You what?

844
00:43:59.458 --> 00:44:01.375
I. uh... Oh. never mind.

845
00:44:02.041 --> 00:44:04.708
[Aki] Oh. I wanted
to ask you something too.

846
00:44:05.500 --> 00:44:06.333
Who…

847
00:44:08.041 --> 00:44:09.750
is it that's teaching you to fight?

848
00:44:11.708 --> 00:44:13.333
[phone buzzing]

849
00:44:16.458 --> 00:44:19.208
HOW TO BEAT A THUG IN A FIGHT

850
00:44:19.291 --> 00:44:21.291
[tense music playing]

851
00:44:21.375 --> 00:44:22.541
Well. I've…

852
00:44:25.625 --> 00:44:27.166
taught myself. [chuckles]

853
00:44:28.458 --> 00:44:30.041
Taught yourself…

854
00:44:32.208 --> 00:44:33.333
See you. then.

855
00:44:42.500 --> 00:44:44.416
[Shimura] Aki's not the one. then.

856
00:44:47.416 --> 00:44:48.708
[music ends]

857
00:44:52.125 --> 00:44:52.958
Hmm.

858
00:44:54.833 --> 00:44:58.333
PASSWORD INCORRECT

859
00:45:05.875 --> 00:45:07.666
-[dance music playing]
-[all whooping]

860
00:45:07.750 --> 00:45:09.500
-Hey! I'm sorry!
-[phone ringing]

861
00:45:09.583 --> 00:45:10.625
More! More!

862
00:45:10.708 --> 00:45:12.166
Sorry! This is me!

863
00:45:12.250 --> 00:45:13.291
-Aw!
-Don't sit down!

864
00:45:13.375 --> 00:45:15.125
Aki. what's up?

865
00:45:15.208 --> 00:45:17.291
Have you been missing me. have you?

866
00:45:17.375 --> 00:45:19.666
Did you alter the password to our channel?

867
00:45:19.750 --> 00:45:22.583
Password? No. why would I do that?

868
00:45:22.666 --> 00:45:24.125
[girl 2] Here. Kanegon. Your drink.

869
00:45:24.208 --> 00:45:26.625
-[Toru] Hang on. Just…
-[girl 3] Come on!

870
00:45:27.916 --> 00:45:30.083
[ominous music playing]

871
00:45:30.166 --> 00:45:32.166
[phone ringing]

872
00:45:35.625 --> 00:45:36.541
Moshi moshi.

873
00:45:36.625 --> 00:45:38.625
It's an emergency. Come back right now.

874
00:45:39.583 --> 00:45:40.625
What emergency?

875
00:45:41.125 --> 00:45:42.916
The Viral Hit account status…

876
00:45:43.875 --> 00:45:45.875
the account's been suspended.

877
00:45:46.458 --> 00:45:49.291
Huh? But we were using it
just a minute ago.

878
00:45:49.375 --> 00:45:50.708
Someone must have hacked it.

879
00:45:50.791 --> 00:45:52.166
Oh my God.

880
00:45:52.250 --> 00:45:53.500
DEPOSIT: 735.300 YEN

881
00:45:53.583 --> 00:45:54.958
That means…

882
00:45:56.750 --> 00:46:00.208
Yes. That means
you're not getting any money.

883
00:46:02.458 --> 00:46:04.541
-[Shimura yells] Ah!
-[Aki] Hey.

884
00:46:05.166 --> 00:46:06.208
What's wrong?

885
00:46:07.625 --> 00:46:08.916
What's going on there?

886
00:46:10.791 --> 00:46:11.708
Shimura?

887
00:46:16.791 --> 00:46:17.958
[groaning]

888
00:46:20.041 --> 00:46:20.958
[gasping]

889
00:46:24.625 --> 00:46:25.541
[whimpering]

890
00:46:34.791 --> 00:46:37.041
[music fades]

891
00:46:37.125 --> 00:46:38.666
[boy 1] This is a warning.

892
00:46:42.250 --> 00:46:43.291
[Aki] Shimura?

893
00:46:43.833 --> 00:46:44.875
Is something wrong?

894
00:46:44.958 --> 00:46:46.333
Are you there. Shimura?!

895
00:46:46.916 --> 00:46:48.958
Can you hear me. Shimura?!

896
00:46:49.041 --> 00:46:51.083
Come on! Please answer me!

897
00:46:51.708 --> 00:46:54.375
[Japanese rock music playing]

898
00:47:03.541 --> 00:47:10.541
VIRAL HIT

899
00:47:15.750 --> 00:47:17.625
[Japanese rock music continues]

900
00:48:27.166 --> 00:48:28.166
[music ends]
